<div class="shadowbox" id="game_rules_shadow_box">
</div>
<div class="shadow-content-container game-rules" id="game_rules">
    <button class="button" id="Close_Rules">X</button>
    <div class="inner-shadow">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="rules bubble-border">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <h2>Objective:</h2>
                            <p>The goal is to obtain a suited-hand that totals 31 points, or to have a hand of higher value than all other players at the showdown.</p>
                            <h2>Play:</h2>
                            <p>All players begin with 3 chips. On each turn, players take one card from either the top of the deck or from the discard pile. A turn ends by discarding a card.</p>
                            <p>Players take turns until one player is satisfied that the cards they hold will likely beat all other players and "knocks" on the table. Once a knock has been made, all other players get one more turn to exchange cards before the showdown where all players reveal their hands and compare values.</p>
                            <h2>Scoring:</h2>
                            <p>Aces: 11 points; Face-cards :10 points; all other cards count their face value</p>
                            <p>If the player who knocked does not have the highest scoring hand at the showdown, they lose a chip to the pot.  However, if they do have the highest scoring hand, the player with the lowest hand loses a chip to the pot instead.</p>
                            <p>If there is a tie for the highest score, the player with the highest-ranking card(s) wins. [e.g. K, Q, 6 (total 26) would beat Q, 9, 7 (also 26)]</p>
                            <p>If at any point a player holds exactly 31 points during the game, or obtains three aces (worth 32 points), the game immediately ends and all other players lose a chip to the pot.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 clearfix">
                            <div class="float-right">
                                <button class="button" id="PlayGame">Got it, let's play!</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
